@Jamie - firstly - if you have not done so, then `docker volume prune` might be a good idea
If you have re-generated the crypto material - then there is at least one change you need to make to the `docker-compose.yml` file:
The value of the environment variable `- FABRIC_CA_SERVER_CA_KEYFILE=/etc/hyperledger/fabric-ca-server-config/...` needs to match the new private key you have generated.

